node.text:
2 YEARS OF THE LITTLE TRASHMAID 🐠💛 Thank you all for reading the comic! I'm very grateful for all the support and will keep doing my best! 
More content and projects to come~

The most recent donation went to @theoceancleanup 🌊
www.patreon.com/thelittletrashmaid 

Next comic will be up next friday~ 

#thelittletrashmaid #trashmaid #mermaid #savetheplanet
